│   8 //                                                                      │
│   9 // This file implements dead code elimination and basic block merging,  │
│ along                                                                       │
│  10 // with a collection of other peephole control flow optimizations.  For │
│ example:                                                                    │
│  11 //                                                                      │
│  12 //   * Removes basic blocks with no predecessors.                       │
│  13 //   * Merges a basic block into its predecessor if there is only one   │
│ and the                                                                     │
│  14 //     predecessor only has one successor.                              │
│  15 //   * Eliminates PHI nodes for basic blocks with a single predecessor. │
│  16 //   * Eliminates a basic block that only contains an unconditional     │
│ branch.                                                                     │
│  17 //   * Changes invoke instructions to nounwind functions to be calls.   │
│  18 //   * Change things like "if (x) if (y)" into "if (x&y)".              │
│  19 //   * etc..                                                            │
│  20 //                                                                      │
│  21                                                                         │
│ //===---------------------------------------------------------------------- │
│ ===//                                                                       │
